Package: Compadre
Title: Kick-ass Analysis of Macroevolutionary Rates of Speciation, Extinction and Sampling using Capture-Mark-Recapture techniques
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jostein",
           family = "Starrfelt",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "josteinstarrfelt@gmail.com")
Description: Estimating rates of speciation, extinction and sampling from a set of fossil occurrances over a given number of intervals. The package allows for inclusion of multiple drivers of all rates as well as estimation of impacts of diversity on the rates (diversity dependence).
License: Do what you want, but please acknowledge my work.
